src/utils/map_osm.py — new interactive OSM map                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                   
  - Real OSM tiles via Folium/Leaflet.js — actual street map you can pan & zoom                                                                    
  - Edges as a single GeoJSON layer (vectorised numpy extraction, no Python loop) — went from 19s → 0.55s                                          
  - Sensors also as one GeoJSON layer instead of 325 individual CircleMarker objects                                                               
  - Shortest path overlay in blue with start/end markers when you pass --path START END                                                            
  - macOS notifications at every major step (load, edge render, done)                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                   
  # Run from repo root                                                                                                         
  .venv/bin/python3 src/utils/map_osm.py                                         
  .venv/bin/python3 src/utils/map_osm.py --path 402365 401129                        
                                                                                                                                                   
  scripts/build_road_graph.py                                                                                                      

    .venv + requirements.txt                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                   
  python3 -m venv .venv                                                                                                                            
  .venv/bin/pip install -r requirements.txt                                                                                                      
  source .venv/bin/activate   